RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

94-1872. State v. Jackson. Cuyahoga County, No. 55758.

Reported at 72 Ohio St.3d 1401, 647 N.E.2d 167. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of this court’s dismissal of this cause for want of prosecution be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective April 25, 1995.
